latestIgtvVideos.title: Shooting workout drills
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Part 2! Practice moves/shots that you know you'll actually do in a game. Don't just practice to practice! Work smart not hard 🙏

• I like to get my shot feeling right before I start my drills. 
• All drills to be done both sides so you're comfortable attacking either side. 
• All drills are 10 makes and not attempts x 2 
• It's okay to miss, as shooters we need to have a short memory. You miss a shot, who gives a shit? Keep it moving. 

It's all about confidence. Put in the work and the results will follow 🗣️
🎵 - Rockstar @dababy
